OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1779527270
OL,3,CBank holiday weekend strikes to
OL,4,Cdisrupt rail services across the West
OL,5,CMidlands
OL,7,FRail passengers are being warned of
OL,8,Fdisruption to services because of a
OL,9,Fstrike over pay.
OL,11,FMembers of the Transport Salaried
OL,12,FStaffs Association (TSSA) will take
OL,13,Findustrial action on Friday and
OL,14,FSaturday, affecting West Midlands
OL,15,FRailway (WMR) and London Northwestern
OL,16,FRailway (LNR).
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
