OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1779527270
OL,3,CBank holiday weekend strikes to
OL,4,Cdisrupt rail services across the West
OL,5,CMidlands
OL,7,FWMR, which operates both railways,
OL,8,Fsaid in a message to passengers: "We
OL,9,Fadvise you to only travel if necessary
OL,10,Fas trains will only run on a small
OL,11,Fnumber of routes.
OL,13,F"Services on both dates will operate
OL,14,Fto a reduced timetable (from 7am) with
OL,15,Fno trains running after 7pm on Friday
OL,16,F22 May and a later 7am start of
OL,17,Fservice on Saturday 23 May."
OL,19,FThe company said that if people do
OL,20,Ftravel, they should be prepared for
OL,21,F"significant disruption" to journeys.
OL,26,@pD@bOUuD@AOUyD@\O]}D@AOU}D@XO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1779527270
OL,3,CBank holiday weekend strikes to
OL,4,Cdisrupt rail services across the West
OL,5,CMidlands
OL,7,FLNR also warned that the industrial
OL,8,Faction will lead to a "very limited"
OL,9,Fservice across its network.
OL,11,FRoutes with a limited service on
OL,12,FFriday and Saturday are Birmingham to
OL,13,FLiverpool and Birmingham ` Northampton
OL,14,F` Milton Keynes ` London Euston ` both
OL,15,Fone train an hour.
OL,17,FRoutes with a limited service on
OL,18,FFriday 22 May and Saturday 23 May are:
OL,20,FCommuters are being advised to check
OL,21,Ffor up to date information on journeys.
OL,26,@pD@WOUpD@dO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1779527270
OL,3,CBank holiday weekend strikes to
OL,4,Cdisrupt rail services across the West
OL,5,CMidlands
OL,7,F"An intolerable situation"
OL,9,FThe dispute involves roster clerks,
OL,10,Fduty train crew managers and control
OL,11,Fstaff.
OL,13,FTSSA general secretary Maryam
OL,14,FEslamdoust said workers were seeking
OL,15,Fparity on pay with those in other
OL,16,Funions.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1779527270
OL,3,CBank holiday weekend strikes to
OL,4,Cdisrupt rail services across the West
OL,5,CMidlands
OL,7,FShe added: "That is an intolerable
OL,8,Fsituation, especially given the fact
OL,9,Fthese are modest demands. Our reps
OL,10,Fhave consulted the membership and they
OL,11,Fremain determined to proceed with
OL,12,Ftheir legitimate action.
OL,14,F"It's now up to the company to come to
OL,15,Ftheir senses and stop these walkouts.
OL,16,FOur union remains open to further
OL,17,Fdiscussions and only takes strike
OL,18,Faction as a last resort."
OL,26,@oD@LOUvD@AOUzD@YO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1779527270
OL,3,CBank holiday weekend strikes to
OL,4,Cdisrupt rail services across the West
OL,5,CMidlands
OL,7,FIan McConnell, Managing Director at
OL,8,FWMR and LNR, said: "We encourage TSSA
OL,9,Fto continue talks with us to reach a
OL,10,Fresolution to this dispute.
OL,12,F"This strike action will cause
OL,13,Fdisruption to our customers with a
OL,14,Fsignificantly reduced timetable in
OL,15,Foperation on both dates.
OL,17,F"We are doing all we can to minimise
OL,18,Fthe impact as far as possible and
OL,19,Fapologise to customers for the
OL,20,Finconvenience.
OL,26,@pD@TOU
