OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1779527270
OL,3,CBank holiday weekend strikes to
OL,4,Cdisrupt rail services across the West
OL,5,CMidlands
OL,7,F"However, where services are running,
OL,8,Fwe advise customers to only travel if
OL,9,Fnecessary and to allow more time for
OL,10,Ftheir journey."
